{
  "chapter": 88,
  "chapter_summary": "第八十八回\"飘忽无踪\"主要讲述两条线索。其一，十大恶人（李大嘴、屠娇娇、哈哈儿、白开心、阴九幽、杜杀）与小鱼儿在树林中会合，苏樱从空心树中现身相迎。十大恶人纷纷离去后，苏樱与小鱼儿深入交谈，苏樱指出十大恶人可能曾诱骗小鱼儿进入魏无牙的老鼠洞，企图借刀杀人。小鱼儿告知苏樱，他曾看到一对神秘夫妇偷走了两包东西——实为两个人，其中包括花无缺。小鱼儿得知后急忙追赶。苏樱决心追随小鱼儿离去。神秘人物从地洞中现身，暗中监视。其二，铁萍姑驾车带着中毒的江玉郎和痴呆的花无缺向山深处行进。白山君与白夫人汇合后，将众人带往隐秘石屋。花无缺精神崩溃如行尸走肉，白山君试图用铁萍姑刺激花无缺，撕衣露体相逼，花无缺却毫无反应。白山君恼羞成怒，欲对铁萍姑施暴。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也学会了屠娇娇的一手？也来挑拨离间了？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他挨了小鱼儿一顿，他心里一直不服气哩。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "不服气又有什么用？哈哈，十个白开心也斗不过一个小鱼儿的，你若是想出气，还是死了这条心吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我又有什么不服气的？有一天狐狸若是被狗吃了，那我才是服气哩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "损人不利己，果然是损人不利己。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "text": "「十大恶人」，也果然名不虚传，我真佩服极了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "text": "名震天下的十大恶人来了，贱妾竟有失远迎，恕罪恕罪。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘千万别客气，咱们这些人是天生的贱骨头，有人对咱们一客气，咱们就以为他要来动坏主意了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走吧，走吧，快走吧。再不走我就受不了啦！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "你受不了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧见这丫头的一身细皮白肉，我简直连口水都快流了出来，但又明知道小鱼儿绝不肯让我吃了她的，再不走我岂非要发疯。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也要走，瞧着这娇滴滴的美人儿，我这光棍也实在有些心动，不如还是快走，眼不见为净，也免得和小鱼儿争风吃醋。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，再不走连和尚都要动凡心了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好我还有一半是女人，否则……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘若做人做腻了，不妨来找我。做鬼有些时比做人有趣得多。这年头漂亮的女鬼，更吃香得很。",
      "tone": "阴森",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "text": "多谢指教，但我现在却活得还蛮有趣哩。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你若是爱上了这个人，用不着多久，就会觉得活着无趣的……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你还要在这里呆多久？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "只怕用不着多久的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你知道在哪里可找得着我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小心些，漂亮的女子若要吃人时，连人头都要吃下去。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "前辈只管放心，我的胃口一向不好，一向是吃素的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "魏麻衣将你吊在树上后，这些人已来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "他们来得正巧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你还是装成不能动的样子来骗我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我本来可不是要骗你的，魏麻衣让我上了一次当，我怎么能就那样放过他，我好歹也得要他知道厉害。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你本来虽不是为了骗我，但后来还是骗了我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你若要这么想，我也没法子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你知道我对你很好，所以就利用这点来骗我，让我为你担心，为你着急，我不顾一切来救你，你反而以此来要挟我说出心里的秘密。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我早就说过，我并不是好人，谁若对我好，准就要倒霉了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "世上大多数人，都生怕自己变得太坏，但你却偏偏相反，你竟好像生怕自己变得太好了，总要做些事来证明你自己不是好东西……这究竟是为了什么呢？这只怕连你自己也想不到的，是么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这只怕是因为我天生是个坏胚子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你可知道，你并没有自己想像中那么坏么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你且说来听听吧。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这只因你从小是跟着那些坏人长大的，所以在你心里面，总觉得自己绝不可能变得太好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "而且，你还认为自己若是变得太好，就有些对不起那些将你养大的人，所以有时你不得不做些坏事来证明自己……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你和我见面还没有几天，就以为很了解我了？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我本来也并不太了解，但见了那些人后，就明白了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那些人真可算是坏人中的天才，已坏得炉火纯青了，他们竟能将一件很卑劣低下，或是很恶毒残酷的事，做得令人反而觉得很有趣。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你用不着这样骂他们，他们可没有得罪你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你难道现在还未发觉，是他们将你诱入那……那老鼠洞去的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "笑话，这才是笑话，他们为何要骗我？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这也许是因为他们已发觉，你并不是和他们一样的坏，他们认为你说不定会反叛他们，所以就故意做下那些标志暗号，将你诱入那老鼠洞，要想借魏无牙之手，将你除去……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "那么我问你，他们既要害死我，方才为何又来救我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这也许是因为他们忽然又觉得你有用了，杀了可惜，也许是因为他们并不想亲手杀死你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "放屁放屁，你说的话，我一个字也不相信。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我也不一定要你相信，只要你多加提防，也就是了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你叫我多加提防？我看你倒真该多加提防才是。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你说的不错，这地方以后只怕真要变成是非之地了，看来我只怕也没法子再在这里呆下去，但是你……你难道发现了什么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "一个被吊在树上的人，瞧见的总要比别人多些的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你究竟瞧见了什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我瞧见两个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "就算瞧见二十个人，也并不是一件什么稀奇的事。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "但这两个人却稀奇得很。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这两个人早已藏在那边的小山石后面了，我的朋友来救我时，他们已经在那里。但他们却好像根本不愿管这边的闲事，等到你和魏麻衣一走进这树林子，他们就立刻飞也似地溜到那边的屋子里去，轻功居然是一等一的高手……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "原来你还是关心我的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你若喜欢自我陶醉，我也没法子，但现在可不是你自我陶醉的时候，那两个人……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不必为我担心，那是一对很有趣的夫妇，常常喜欢做一些自作聪明的事，男的一个还好些，女的一个总认为自己比别人都聪明得多，其实却是个神经病。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "自以为比别人聪明的人，大多是有些毛病的，但我却是例外，只因为我的确比别人聪明得多。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他们已走了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "不但走了，而且还带走了两大包东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "什么时候走的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "就在刚刚你笑得最开心的时候。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "现在，只怕你也笑不出了吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他们偷走的不是两包东西，是两个人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "偷走了两个人？是活人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不能算活人，但也不能算死人，只能算是两个半死不活的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "看来这夫妻两人的确是有点毛病……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但他们却等于帮了你一个忙。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他们偷去的两个人中，有一个就是要和你拼命的仇人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你……你……你是说……花无缺？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你说花无缺被人偷走了？你为什么不早说？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我怎知他被人偷走？你为何不早些告诉我？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "不错，我为何不早些告诉你！我为何不拦住他们……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是前辈们回来了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "是我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你放心，你的玉郎现在正好好躺在这里哩。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冷……冷，冷死我了。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "热，简直热得要命。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "那丫头也不知下了什么毒，竟将这孩子折磨成如此模样。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "这小子和咱们既非亲，又非故，只不过是慕名投奔而来的，你又何苦为他如此难受？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "傻老头子，你以为我真是为了他难受么？我只不过是觉得那丫头的手段太厉害了而已，你瞧咱们这位花公子……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "这姓花的如此模样，才实在是令人担心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "你看他是真的已变得如此模样，还是装出来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "这倒难说得很！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "他现在是发冷还是发热？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "他现在只觉全身都在疼，也不知是……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "听说你是从移花宫中逃出来的，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "你……你既然已知道，为何还要来问我？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "既是如此，我就要借你的身子一用。",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "无……无妨，前……前辈只管借去吧！",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你认得这女子是谁么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你还不认得她？好，我再叫你瞧清楚些！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你眼见你的同门这般模样，还是不闻不问，也不怕将你们「移花宫」上上下下的人全都丢光了脸么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好，你既不怕丢人，我索性让你人再丢大些。",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    }
